data.title: Top 5 Plays of Week 5: Jjonak's Instant Sleep Dart Is on Target
data.description: The first week of Hero Pool produced a spectacle of pure chaos in Washington, D.C. We got a lot of Sombra play, which meant a lot of Jjonak hitting unthinkable Sleep Darts. Winston got his time to shine and Roar made sure to capitalize on Eichenwalde. Meanwhile, Blass Doomfist continued to reign supreme.

data.title: Full Match | Boston Uprising vs Atlanta Reign | Overwatch League 2020 | Week 5 | Day 2
data.description: Week 5 of the 2020 Overwatch League season is live from Washington D.C. on March 7 and March 8 on YouTube Gaming. The two-day homestand features the Toronto Defiant, Florida Mayhem, Paris Eternal, Houston Outlaws, Boston Uprising, Philadelphia Fusion, New York Excelsior and Atlanta Reign. data.title: Match complet | New York Excelsior contre Florida Mayhem | OWL 2020 | Semaine 4 | Jours 1
data.description: L'Overwatch League prend ses quartiers  Houston,  suivre en direct sur Youtube Gaming. S'affronteront les New York Excelsior, Florida Mayhem, Toronto Defiant, Atlanta Reign, London Spitfire, Bonston Uprising, Philadelphia Fusion et Paris Eternal.
